*** LIVE RADIO BROADCAST ***
Listen to the best swiss radio stations: SRF 1, SRF 2 Kultur, SRF 3, SRF 4 News, SRF Virus, SRF Musikwelle, RTS La Première, RTS Espace 2, RTS Couleur 3, RTS Option Musique, Swiss Pop, Swiss Jazz, Swiss Classic, NRJ and many others!

With this app you can listen to a huge variety of radio stations: from sports to news and music.

Radio CH - Swiss Radio / Schweizer Radio / Radio Suisse is the best way to listen to the radio on your iPod Touch, iPhone and iPad.

You can listen the best radio stations of your country or of your homeland when you are abroad.  

With Radio CH - Swiss Radio / Schweizer Radio / Radio Suisse you can: 
- Listen to the best radio stations in Switzerland;
- Zapping stations in an easy way;
- Listen radios in the background;  
- Listen radio with Air-Play; 

There may be some stations that do not work because their stream is offline.This application is optimized for 3G networks and Wi-Fi.

Radio CH - Swiss Radio / Schweizer Radio / Radio Suisse gives you the best experience in listening to radio stations!

